Carey Hayes -LRB- born April 21 , 1961 in Portland , Oregon -RRB- is an American screenwriter and producer .
He is the twin brother of Chad Hayes .
They are partners in the business and have written most of their work together .
The two also appeared in Doublemint Gum commercials in their early years of acting in the 1980s .
He has written episodes of Baywatch and Baywatch Nights and has written and co-produced the TV show The Crow : Stairway to Heaven .